column8: Cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of snow showers, most likely this evening. Winds southeasterly 35 to 45 km/h.

Cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of snow showers, most likely in the early morning. Winds southeasterly 25 to 35 km/h tending easterly 20 to 30 km/h early in the morning then becoming light in the early afternoon.
Partly cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm in the late morning and afternoon. Light winds.

Partly cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon. Winds southerly 15 to 20 km/h tending southeasterly during the morning then becoming light during the day.
Cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm. Light winds becoming northwest to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h during the morning.
Partly cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers. Winds northeast to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending southeasterly during the day.
Partly cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of showers. Winds southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h.
